{"tid":1454659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人機干擾 倫敦吉域機場連關兩天 20181221","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:58:26.000Z","uid":282551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86c74cd7764aeee2d1b13d3d4dbd5c8b0b80f887","tid":1454659,"uid":282551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"無人機干擾 倫敦吉域機場連關兩天<br />\n20181221<br />\n【明報專訊】英國倫敦吉域（Gatwick）機場周三（19日）晚起因有數架無人機在機場附近飛行，為安全計暫時關閉，機場在聖誕前旺季連續兩天關閉令約12萬人受影響。機場稱確保安全之前，機場都不會重開。警方稱沒證據顯示與恐怖主義有關，但認為是蓄意干擾機場。事件突顯無人機對民航機的威脅。英國航空管理人員工會昨發聲明，稱他們過去一直呼籲加強對無人機管制，但卻屢遭政府漠視，促機場要加裝反無人機措施<br />\n<br />\n軍事等級的信號干擾能阻止無人機，卻也影響到航班<br />\n20190114<br />\n【科技新報】目前全球對小型無人機的監管，主要是從登記註冊和飛行區域限制等相對較基礎的方式。蓋維克機場負責人 Damien Trower 表示，機場會在飛機起飛的區域設置禁飛標誌，還測試多種不同技術方案，以應付無人機違規飛行，但目前沒有單一商業解決方案可限制無人機在機場區域使用。<br />\n<br />\n英國皇家空軍的反無人機系統在測試、監控和停止無人機方面都非常有效，但即使部署軍事裝置，也很難徹底解決問題。目前美國軍方大約使用 20 種系統對抗戰場無人機襲擊，之所以使用 20 多種，是因為沒有單一系統能有效控制。<br />\n<br />\n各大無人機公司推出的安全方案是在特定區域設置虛擬的禁飛區，該區域內無法定位和遠程操控，但如果用戶使用手動控制，仍然可飛行。為了阻止無人機，機場聯合警方和通訊部門設立更複雜的雷達系統，但軍事等級的信號干擾系統雖能有效阻止無人機，也會影響到一般客機。<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/01/14/can-airports-ever-make-themselves-safe-from-drones/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2Fcan-airports-ever-make-themselves-safe-from-drones%2F&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQzmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=84e27e18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/01/14/can-airports-ever-make-themselves-safe-from-drones/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20181221/s00014/1545329566467/%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE-%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%90%89%E5%9F%9F%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%A3%E9%97%9C%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20181221%2Fs00014%2F1545329566467%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E6%2593%25BE-%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%2590%2589%25E5%259F%259F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQzmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=c24d6422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20181221%2Fs00014%2F1545329566467%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E6%2593%25BE-%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%2590%2589%25E5%259F%259F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9&h=c8c08edb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20181221/s00014/1545329566467/%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE-%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%90%89%E5%9F%9F%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%A3%E9%97%9C%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9</a>"},{"pid":"dce6f336414a26bb3c730a5601dc072cef06b32c","tid":1454659,"uid":282551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e16173ed60864ebdcded3a7f999addaea9f64ad","tid":1454659,"uid":282551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:04:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c3c7bef3114560555471678fbbca95f59bccdbe1","tid":1454659,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb5cd7847b47bbdd36e2eb06e3c60b3729c6f7d","tid":1454659,"uid":282551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8373eee8d54f523d557d22fe3a12e294d420b44","tid":1454659,"uid":282551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:05:03.000Z",